msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgate ca tathāgatasāvake ca. "
msgstr "The Realized One and a disciple of the Realized One. "

# NOTE: Note dvīsu is missing here, it is included in BB.
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.4"
msgid "Imesu kho, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavatīti. "
msgstr "When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward these people they keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much bad karma. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.91, sc137.2
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.1"
msgid "Dvīsu, bhikkhave, sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati. "
msgstr "When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward two people they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.2"
msgid "Katamesu dvīsu? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.3"
msgid "Tathāgate ca tathāgatasāvake ca. "
msgstr "The Realized One and a disciple of the Realized One. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.4"
msgid "Imesu kho, bhikkhave, dvīsu sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti. "
msgstr "When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward these two people they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.138" id="138"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.5"
msgid "138 "
msgstr "138 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc138.1
msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“There are these two things. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.3"
msgid "Sacittavodānañca na ca kiñci loke upādiyati. "
msgstr "Cleaning your own mind, and not grasping at anything in the world. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the two things.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.139" id="139"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.5"
msgid "139 "
msgstr "139 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc139.1
msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“There are these two things. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.3"
msgid "Kodho ca upanāho ca. "
msgstr "Anger and hostility. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the two things.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.140" id="140"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.5"
msgid "140 "
msgstr "140 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc140.1
msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“There are these two things. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.3"
msgid "Kodhavinayo ca upanāhavinayo ca. "
msgstr "Dispelling anger and dispelling hostility. "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the two things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
